title: Bruce Springsteen | The Wet Coast
description:
Northern California is hit with a huge storm and torrential rain after declaring a drought emergency last week, while Democrats are inching towards a deal on the spending bill. Stephen sits down with Bruce Springsteen to talk about his new book “Renegades: Born in the USA,” and what it was like working from podcast to page with Former President Barack Obama.
